videos.description: On Washington State's first drive they fumble then followed by Iowa State throwing an interception on their first possession.
videos.headline: WSU and ISU exchange turnovers to start game

videos.description: Washington State defensive back Marcus Strong gets the INT and runs it back, however he was called for taunting taking away the TD.
videos.headline: WSU gets pick-6 called back for taunting

videos.description: After the interception, WSU capitalizes with Gardener Minshew finding a wide open Renard Bell for the 22-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Minshew finds a wide-open receiver for the TD

videos.description: Gardner Minshew avoids the pass rush and spins out of the pocket, then is able to dive into the end zone for the 7-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Minshew scrambles for wild running TD

videos.description: Iowa State quarterback Brock Purdy runs through the hole and dives into the end zone for the 9-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: ISU QB comes right back and gets his own rushing TD

videos.description: Washington State wide receiver Dezmon Patmon goes way up in the air to haul in the 9-yard touchdown for a 21-7 lead.
videos.headline: WSU receiver makes spectacular TD catch

videos.description: Iowa State defender Eyioma Uwazurike is ejected for targeting causing Iowa State coach Matt Campbell to go crazy as he disagrees with the call.
videos.headline: Iowa State coach loses mind after targeting call

videos.description: Iowa State running back David Montgomery goes through defenders for the 8-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Montgomery powers way into the end zone for TD

videos.description: Iowa State wide receiver Hakeem Butler shows off the skills with a sweet, one-handed catch.
videos.headline: Butler goes up to make one-handed catch

videos.description: After a huge third down conversion WSU running back Max Borghi runs through the hole and finds the end zone for the 10-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Borghi runs through defenders for TD

videos.description: Brock Purdy dives into the end zone for the 1-yard touchdown but Iowa State is unable to tie the game with a 2-point conversion.
videos.headline: Purdy dives short TD, Iowa State fails on 2-pt conversion
